creator: Onii-chan studio
descriptionHtml:
I'm gonna ask you something.

Have you ever wished for onii-chan sounds for your mobile phone?

If your answer is YES then I present you Onii-chan Soundboard .!!

This application offers a unique collection of short, quick and funny onii-chan sounds to use in almost any situation. You can assign the voice clips as ringtones, notification sounds or alarms. Besides, you can even share them with your friends and have a laugh!!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Hello, people! 💙🌴
First of all I hope that you all are well in these difficult moments that plague the world, I hope that this update will offer you some good moments and a good laugh.

What's new in this version:
🔹 The size of the application has been reduced.
🔹 25 New Onii-chan sounds.
🔹 Error fixing.
